Don't let the clothes define your silhouette! Take control of your curves with the Levi's Womens 311 Shaping Skinny. This five-pocket jean features a mid-rise and sleek skinny fit for a leg-lengthening silhouette. The front has a specially designed panel that holds you in for a tummy-slimming effect. Signature arcuate stitch highlights the back pockets. Belt loop waistband with brand patch at the back waist. Zip-fly and button closure.Material breakdown for washes are listed highest to lowest based on cotton percentage. Soft Tamburitza, Pumice: 83% cotton, 15% polyester, 2% elastane. Darkest Sky: 81% cotton, 17% polyester, 2% elastane. Hawaii Ocean, Maui Views, Oahu Morning Dew: 79% cotton, 19% polyester, 2% elastane. Grey Slumber: 70% cotton, 20% polyester, 8% viscose, 2% elastane. Soft Black: 69% cotton, 23% polyester, 7% viscose, 1% elastane. Malbec Twill: 63% cotton, 31% viscose, 4% polyester, 2% elastane. Secret Admirer: 60% cotton, 22% viscose, 16% polyester, 2% elastane. Machine wash, tumble dry.
